org.cpsolver.coursett.sectioning

Class SctModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.coursett.sectioning.SctModel

  • public class SctModel
extends Object
    A model representing student enrollments of a course. Branch & bound algorithm is used to propose best possible enrollment of all students into the given course.
    Version:
    CourseTT 1.3 (University Course Timetabling)
